BT /F2 9.50 Tf 0.420 0.420 0.460 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 309.50 Tm (ON SCREEN) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 293.50 Tm (A definition, plus a two-column diagram contrasting a traditional web app returning HTML with a web service) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 280.00 Tm (returning JSON.) Tj ET
0.720 0.720 0.760 rg 58.00 266.50 3.00 49.00 re f
BT /F2 9.50 Tf 0.040 0.340 0.780 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 255.50 Tm (SAY \(read this aloud\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 239.50 Tm (So let's nail down what a web service actually is. A web service is a way for two applications to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 224.30 Tm (talk to each other and exchange data over a network - and it does not matter what languages they) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 209.10 Tm (are written in. A Java app can talk to a Python app, which can talk to a phone app. The key word,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 193.90 Tm (again, is data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 173.70 Tm (Look at the two columns on screen, because this contrast is the whole idea. On the left is a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 158.50 Tm (traditional web app. You ask it for a page, and it sends back HTML - a full web page, designed for) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 143.30 Tm (a human's eyes, with colours and layout. On the right is a web service. You ask it for something,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 128.10 Tm (and it sends back pure data - usually JSON - designed for another program to read and use, not) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 112.90 Tm (for a human to look at.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 92.70 Tm (Let me give you an analogy. A traditional web app is like a fully plated, decorated dish served at) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 77.50 Tm (your table - ready to eat, made to look nice. A web service is like raw ingredients delivered to a) Tj ET
