BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 696.60 Tm (If they remember only ONE, make it stateless. Each request stands completely on its own; the server) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 682.20 Tm (does not remember you between calls. Use an analogy: it is like a vending machine - you put in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 667.80 Tm (everything needed each time, and it does not care who you are or what you bought before. That one) Tj ET
