BT /F2 9.50 Tf 0.040 0.340 0.780 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 382.40 Tm (SAY \(read this aloud\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 366.40 Tm (A quick look ahead, because today's app has two weaknesses we will fix next time. Right now our) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 351.20 Tm (data lives in a list in memory - so it vanishes the moment the app stops. And if you ask for a) Tj ET
