BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 754.00 Tm (building a REST controller.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 733.80 Tm (Let me run through them quickly. At-RestController - marks the controller, returns data as JSON.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 718.60 Tm (At-RequestMapping - sets the base address. At-GetMapping, PostMapping, PutMapping,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 703.40 Tm (DeleteMapping - one for each of the four verbs, read, create, update, delete. At-PathVariable -) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 688.20 Tm (grabs a value from the address. At-RequestParam - grabs a query value after the question mark.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 673.00 Tm (At-RequestBody - turns incoming JSON into a Java object. And at-ResponseStatus - sets the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 657.80 Tm (status code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 637.60 Tm (Ten labels. If you know what these ten do, you can build any REST API. That is genuinely the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 622.40 Tm (whole toolkit.) Tj ET
