BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 483.50 Tm (nouns and verbs, what those status code numbers mean, and which annotations build a controller.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 468.30 Tm (That is a real, solid foundation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 448.10 Tm (Now let's open the lab and build the Student CRUD API together, one endpoint at a time - exactly) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 432.90 Tm (the way real teams do it: write a method, run it, test it, move on. Don't just watch me - code along,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 417.70 Tm (because this stuff only truly clicks when your own fingers type it. Let's build it.) Tj ET
